      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jan 2005 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://www.suzukinet.com/posts/2005-01-01-%E9%8A%80%E5%BA%A7%E5%B0%8F%E6%82%AA%E9%AD%94%E6%97%A5%E8%A8%98/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/ASIN/4872878418/suzukinetcom-22/ref=nosim&#34;&gt;「銀座小悪魔日記?元銀座ホステスの過激すぎる私生活」&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/ASIN/4776790688/suzukinetcom-22/ref=nosim&#34;&gt;「ふたつの蜜月 ~銀座小悪魔日記」&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;
